===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|sittan}}, from {{proto|Germanic|sitjanan|lang=en}}, from *{{term||set-}}, from {{proto|Indo-European|sed-|sit|lang=en}}. Cognate with German {{term|sitzen}}, Dutch {{term|zitten}}, Swedish {{term|sitta}}; and with Irish {{term|suigh}}, Russian {{term|сидеть}}.

